  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "The dev experience for Hardhat windows users is not always up to standards, case in point; the official Hardhat Docker plugin is already quite extensively leveraged in other important plugins such as this most recent [Starknet Hardhat plugin](https://github.com/Shard-Labs/starknet-hardhat-plugin/issues/new).\r\n\r\nI can tell you were aware of the issue when developing the plugin: https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/blob/1ae89c406b702e11657bc7ff4142dcfa4fe35631/packages/hardhat-docker/src/hardhat-docker.ts#L37-L41\r\n\r\nBesides fixing this particular case, it would be nice to secure a commitment from the Nomic Labs Hardhat team to maintain the high cross-platform standards that we are used to expect from your tools",
